Roche reports a strong performance in the first half 2017


Group sales CHF 26.3 bn (+5% at constant exchange rates)
Pharmaceuticals sales CHF 20.5 bn (+5%), driven mainly by Tecentriq, Ocrevus and Perjeta
Diagnostics sales CHF 5.8 bn (+5%), primarily due to immunodiagnostics
Outlook for 2017 raised




