Hoffmann-La Roche

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Roche Holding AG





Type

Aktiengesellschaft


Traded as
SIX: ROG, OTCQX: RHHBY


Industry
Pharmaceuticals


Founded
1896; 121 years ago (1896)


Founder
Fritz Hoffmann-La Roche


Headquarters
Basel, Switzerland



Key people

Christoph Franz (Chairman of the board),
Severin Schwan (CEO),
